  "url": "https://www.ada.lk/breaking_news/\u0d86\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dd4-\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dda-\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db8\u0dda-\u0db6\u0db9\u0dbb-\u0d87\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca-\u0dc3\u0d82\u0da0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7-\u0db6\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dcf/11-396504",
  "time_ut": 1661149784,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d86\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0db1\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dda \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db8\u0dda \u0db6\u0db9\u0dbb \u0d87\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0d82\u0da0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Tourists are disturbed by wasps on the nine-arch bridge",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Residents say that local and foreign tourists are often attacked by the wasps on the pillars of the Ella Demodara nine-arch bridge on the Udara railway line.",
        "It is said that the wasps that have been stuck on the stone pillars of the nine-arch bridge for a long time sting the tourists who are watching Siri on the bridge because the animals scatter due to the attacks of hawks and the shock caused by the train.",
        "Local and foreign tourists who are often attacked by wasps are admitted to Demodara, Ella, Bandarawela and Badulla hospitals for treatment and the local residents have informed the relevant authorities several times but they say that no remedy has been received so far."
      ],
